{"tid":1682124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地應該針對DQ事件發起一次大型行動","createTime":"2019-10-30T00:55:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T03:21:21.000Z","uid":78020,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a131e3d33c877c1881828f31bb71e129696bbf04","tid":1682124,"uid":78020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T00:55:57.000Z","msg":"可能好多人會覺得，之鋒被DQ係意料之內，而且佢要被DQ先可以發揮佢係國際戰線嘅最大作用<br />\n但如果香港人自己唔對DQ事件作出反應，外國政客會點睇？會唔會影響左國際戰線嘅工作？<br />\n相反，如果我地表態反抗任何剝奪政治權利嘅事件，係可以同返係出面做緊遊說工作嘅手足裏應外合，夾實外國勢力，百利而無一害<br />\n大家有無咩意見"},{"pid":"919785a21febb19753c7b614ba5ca2f2246dcec2","tid":1682124,"uid":95588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T00:56:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b962293aae59d2794c40d3a77c5bfe3d255a6bf9","tid":1682124,"uid":78020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T00:57:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17f6320ade1601d4d19d44674a5bd8a797a0ac22","tid":1682124,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T00:57:46.000Z","msg":"絕對要"},{"pid":"2898e786fc182826e30c94b393f4e183a14495b3","tid":1682124,"uid":284264,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T00:58:07.000Z","msg":"dq係選舉問題<br />\n更係外國戰線<br />\n所以行動只能和理非"},{"pid":"0069adcf4f26baed04d3ffcc919042ab2aa16c02","tid":1682124,"uid":78020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T00:59:38.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b7eb4ce15c35f5d72caf0830efe421a9ab4ab5c1","tid":1682124,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T00:59:58.000Z","msg":"絕對要"},{"pid":"85eb577ab163e311b3cb53b1c45c3200a13ed044","tid":1682124,"uid":78020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2898e786fc182826e30c94b393f4e183a14495b3","tid":1682124,"uid":284264,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T00:58:07.000Z","msg":"dq係選舉問題<br />\n更係外國戰線<br />\n所以行動只能和理非"},"citedBy":